; Coverage test for filters.cc line 1166
; Test posts_as_equity filter where some amounts are zero.
; When amount.is_zero() returns true, the create_post_from_amount
; functor returns early (line 1165-1166).
; Assets:Cash has a zero balance so its equity post is skipped.

2024/01/01 Opening
    Assets:Cash    $100.00
    Equity:Opening

2024/01/02 Zero out
    Equity:Opening    $100.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/03 Other
    Assets:Savings    $50.00
    Equity:Opening

test equity
2024/01/03 Opening Balances
    Assets:Savings                            $50.00
    Equity:Opening
end test
